# Overview

Log and Console output sections should be separated clearly in the following format
All HEADERS should be bold
MAJOR HEADERS BLUE
MINOR HEADERS GREEN

<Major Headers>
============================================
     HEADER or TITLE
============================================

</Major Headers>

<Minor Headers>
--------------------------------------------
     MINOR HEADER or TITLE
--------------------------------------------

</Minor Headers>
